{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"塔辛，米目，"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"這些是明白的經典中的節文。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"因為他們不信道，你或許氣得要死。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"如果我意欲，我將從天上降示他們一個蹟象，他們就為它而俯首貼耳。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"每逢有新的記念從至仁主降示他們，他們都背棄它。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他們確已否認真理，他們所嘲笑的事的結局，將降臨他們。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"難道他們沒有觀察大地嗎？我使各種優良的植物在大地上繁衍。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"此中確有一個蹟象，但他們大半是不信道的。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"你的主確是萬能的，確是至慈的。"}]}